license: MIT
keywords:
  - climate
  - children
  - health
  - vulnerability
  - UNICEF
  - CCRI
  - open-data
  - geospatial
  - OpenStreetMap
abstract: >
  An open-source pipeline that produces facility-level 0-100 Child Climate
  Risk Scores for schools and health clinics worldwide, combining climate,
  air-quality, population, and geospatial data to help decision-makers
  prioritise which facilities to protect first.
